Good evening, David,
Please schedule your resources to attend this property and complete the nex=
t steps in this claim process. As below:

Contents Appraisal
Contents Removal
Full decontamination clean upstairs level.
Strip-out dwelling to provide visibility for scope of works

I am not expecting you to be able to allocate your resources tomorrow morni=
ng. Please provide our customer, Chris and myself with the earliest possibl=
e time that you can begin this process.
Many thanks for your continued attention to these requests.
Regards,
Grant.


[cid:daa01111-8667-45f9-8f11-0bfde80cb0a4@AUSP282.PROD.OUTLOOK.COM]
Grant Metson
Regional Manager - House Assessing
Phone 021 744 288
Level 5, 136 Fanshawe Street,
PO Box 90347, Auckland 1142

