 and shared with you.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"xmsonormal" style=
=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1">
<strong><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,san=
s-serif">Structural Engineer Guidelines</span></strong><span style=3D"font-=
size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">: I previously aske=
d about guidelines for paying a structural engineer, as
 per the provision for claim preparation. Could you please provide these, a=
s I believe an independent assessment should precede any repair work?<span =
class=3D"xapple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><span style=3D"color:#0070C0"=
>Agreed. It will precede repair work =E2=80=93 but
 the site must be cleaned and cleared first so the structure can be properl=
y assessed.<span class=3D"xapple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span></spa=
n><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#0070C0">&nbsp;</span><span style=
=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p></o:p=
></span></li></ul>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">One of the things I=
 should underline is that with any claim of this nature there are multiple =
cleaning processes which occur =E2=80=93 these are normally as follows:</sp=
an><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-ser=
if"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p>=
</o:p></span></p>
</div>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0in" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"xmsolistparagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;m=
so-list:l1 level1 lfo2">
<b><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Initial fire/smoke clean:</span></u>=
</b><span class=3D"xapple-converted-space"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"=
>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">to allow for detailed=
 and accurate structural assessment. To reduce
 smoke and other claim related odors. To prevent further contamination and =
spreading of soot, etc.</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&=
quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"xmsolist=
paragraph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo=
2">
<b><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Subsequent and multiple site cleans =
during repair works:</span></u></b><span class=3D"xapple-converted-space"><=
span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-siz=
e:11.0pt">this is a constant process of keeping
 the site tidy.</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cal=
ibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"xmsolistparagrap=
h" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2">
<b><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Final professional clean:</span></u>=
</b><span class=3D"xapple-converted-space"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"=
>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">this is completed bef=
ore the home is re-occupied.</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-fam=
ily:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p></o:p></span></li></ol>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p>=
</o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">My apologies =E2=80=
=93 I was not clear enough to explain that the cleaning process is not sing=
ular and final =E2=80=93 it is part of an ongoing process as described abov=
e.</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sa=
ns-serif"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p>=
</o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please let me know =
when we can issue instructions for Asset Managers to continue with the next=
 steps in the process provided.</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-=
family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Best Regards,</span=
><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif=
"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
